{"tid":232422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美加等地中國留學生與中國政府關係密切　禁絕校內一切反中言論","createTime":"2017-05-06T17:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T17:54:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f1222daf32de6634f3587a772c85bdbf3af2aa2","tid":232422,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/06131507/dfbdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F06131507%2Fdfbdb.jpg&h=b7465bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 2017-5-6 13:13字體： A A A<br />\n《紐約時報》報道，中國學生學者聯誼會（Chinese Students and Scholars Association）各分會在西方校園內施加過大的影響力，並與中國政府關係密切，打壓當地校園一切批評中國政府的言論。報道亦指出，隨著在美國的中國留學生越來越多，他們的學費對於學校是一筆龐大的收入，因而有能力向校方施壓。另外，中國政府亦期望提升CSSA對共產黨的忠誠和愛國主義。<br />\n<br />\n報道指CSSA的多個分會均與中國駐當地領事館有聯繫。加拿大移民官員指，加拿大滿地可協和大學（Concordia University）的CSSA分會領導人，有使用中國政府的資金，向中國外交官提供親民主內地生的信息。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述英國布里斯托大學（University of Bristol）的國際發展教授Jeffrey Henderson表示，曾經在2014年獲英國杜蘭大學（Durham University）邀請，，在一個關於「雨傘運動」的研討會上發言，他當時便收到來自CSSA會長的電郵，指中國駐倫敦大使館關注是次事件，並不希望研討會干擾香港與中國的和諧關係。Henderson亦發現研討會的問答環節已受嚴格控制，只有通過審查的書面問題方可提問。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：片段截圖、紐約時報網頁截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/214819/《紐時》：英美加等地中國留學生與中國政府關係/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F214819%2F%E3%80%8A%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%9A%E8%8B%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%8A%A0%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725IzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=efd4c0f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/214819/《紐時》：英美加等地中國留學生與中國政府關係/</a>"},{"pid":"39bb1093a135f36a6d891efd5b247f8e1586549f","tid":232422,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c0682094e47d5c4ebbc660d3062446cc62fef9","tid":232422,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T20:22:10.000Z","msg":"等trump做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1045a61497d0bb2e723157b2d02eaaed6ba0894b","tid":232422,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f597edcf40e225beb98b0f7b0f08b2f14cb90524","tid":232422,"uid":86418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:54:24.000Z","msg":"英國每間大學都有 CSSA, 裡面笠笠亂"}]}